8th July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 5 Highlights

Stage 5 is one for the sprinters covering the flat 189km between Arras and Amiens. Previous winners here include Andre Darrigade and Mario Cipollini - which of today's top fast-men will add their names to the list? Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
